---
title: Montreal Spiced Pork with DIY Zucchini Noodles
description: We're crazy for zoodles and now you can be too! DIY zucchini squash noodles get a tumble in a velvety dreamy cream sauce and topped with Montreal spiced pork tenderloin. You won't believe how easy this all comes together!

